DISCLAIMER AND WARNING:

This software performs destructive operations on macOS applications by design.
The "destroy-redeploy" process completely removes and reinstalls applications,
which may result in:

- Loss of application preferences and settings
- Loss of application data not backed up by the tool
- Temporary unavailability of applications during the process
- Potential system instability if interrupted during critical operations

USERS ARE STRONGLY ADVISED TO:

1. Backup all important data before using this software
2. Test the software in non-production environments first
3. Understand the implications of complete application removal
4. Ensure they have administrator privileges and stable internet connection
5. Read all prompts and confirmations carefully before proceeding

The authors and contributors of this software assume NO RESPONSIBILITY for:

- Data loss of any kind
- System damage or instability
- Lost productivity or business disruption
- Any other direct or indirect damages resulting from use of this software

USE THIS SOFTWARE AT YOUR OWN RISK AND DISCRETION.

This software is intended for advanced users, system administrators, and
developers who understand the implications of forceful application
reinstallation. It is not recommended for casual users or those unfamiliar
with macOS system administration.

By using this software, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and
agreed to these terms and accept full responsibility for any consequences
of its use.
